S.FORM: Corey Benjamin nilacul Corey Benjamin nalecuh i Compton, California, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Corey Benjamin i 1998 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 28, namapili' tu nu Chicago Bulls putiput. nalecuhan ciniza i 2 a bulad 24 a demiad, 1978 a mihcaan, Corey Benjamin, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
